    "summary": "A RESOLUTION COMMEMORATING AND CELEBRATING THE 155TH ANNIVERSARY OF THE FOUNDING OF ALCORN STATE UNIVERSITY, AMERICA'S FIRST HISTORICALLY BLACK LAND-GRANT UNIVERSITY, THE OLDEST LAND-GRANT INSTITUTION IN THE STATE OF MISSISSIPPI, AND A PREMIER RESEARCH AND TEACHING INSTITUTION OF HIGHER LEARNING."
